{"tid":909191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不堪頑疾　老夫婦燒炭雙亡","createTime":"2018-11-20T07:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T08:29:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b7ab6f4ff957dfcc897c46786b8a05d1f1e5879","tid":909191,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181120/20550043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F20550043&d=GLHxB1Bl6fk81vWTn2Ta64zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c61d4180\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F20550043&h=41a722a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181120/20550043</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月20日 <br />\n<br />\n不堪頑疾　老夫婦燒炭雙亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181120/large/20la6p32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181120%2Flarge%2F20la6p32.jpg&h=9681fe76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n探員昨到場撿走多袋證物調查。黎家駒攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一對年老夫婦，疑不堪頑疾纏身，在天水圍住所燒炭自殺亡，昨午其女兒到訪始揭發。警方調查後列作自殺協定，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n死者夫婦姓呂（75歲）及姓姚（87歲），居於天恩邨恩樂樓一單位，其中呂伯患有眼疾及行動不便，需要坐輪椅，其妻子則患抑鬱症長達10年。據悉，呂氏夫婦育有五名子女，其後子女結婚搬出，剩兩老在家，但子女經常返回探望。疑兩老有感體弱多病，不堪頑疾纏身，姚婦曾向子女透露想死。前日中午兒子返回探望兩老，並無異樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女兒探望揭發<br />\n<br />\n昨午1時許，59歲女兒返回探望，發現大門反鎖及拍門無人應，懷疑兩老出事報警。警員及消防員到場破門入屋，發現客廳有一盆燒過的炭，呂伯坐輪椅倒斃廚房，其妻子則死在睡房。警員在屋內沒有撿獲遺書，案列自殺協定，死因有待剖驗。<br />\n<br />\n按《侵害人身罪條例》，現時自殺不屬刑事罪行，但自殺協定屬《殺人罪行條例》，即指任何人若與另一人制訂自殺協定並按協定行事，雖然不算謀殺罪，但當事人已經干犯誤殺罪，罪成最高可判終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張家豪、黎家駒  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n馬時亨續掌港鐵半年尋CEO<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n黃大仙再現鼠傳人戊肝個案"},{"pid":"d71998baad5587997bb8408d62f3438af8845765","tid":909191,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"人地老夫老妻想一齊死關人撚事咩<br />\n自殺協定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 罪成係咪鞭屍呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e341e52370a340a2a9c4a5561a89d0247fd2f2b","tid":909191,"uid":3028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"16歲屌28歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31dacb98a052ebcb8a05b2d0cdcb4e1aca176013","tid":909191,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"小朋友屌大姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6294c6635945dd4baf96b6b631175f3b72a718f","tid":909191,"uid":22974,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aa00baeeb3fd5001d45baa57c08a221565424c0","tid":909191,"uid":59952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:12:33.000Z","msg":"都可能好事黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到啲仔女冇哂顧慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔駛再擔心佢地"},{"pid":"6784b006614418b407db2180e35fe91cb08788f9","tid":909191,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e341e52370a340a2a9c4a5561a89d0247fd2f2b","tid":909191,"uid":3028,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"16歲屌28歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6704ee4b3a8ae9915ac20808f972ff68a7d744","tid":909191,"uid":29702,"like":0,"d